{"id": 7047, "source": "pestle", "subject": "chemistry", "course": null, "level": "HL", "paper": "2", "year": "2017", "session": "17M", "subtopic": "14-1-covalent-bonding-and-electron-domain-and-molecular-geometries", "title": "17M.2.HL.TZ1.8", "topic_id": "14", "source_url": "https://pestle.pages.dev/app/", "question_html": "<div class=\"specification\">\n<p>There is concern about damage done to the ozone layer in the stratosphere by jet-propelled aircraft.</p>\n</div><div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px;\">\n<p>Formulate two equations to show how nitrogen(II) oxide, NO, catalyses the destruction of ozone.</p>\n<div class=\"marks\">[2]</div>\n<div class=\"question_part_label\">a.</div>\n</div><div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px;\">\n<p>Suggest why the loss of ozone is an international environmental concern.</p>\n<div class=\"marks\">[2]</div>\n<div class=\"question_part_label\">b.</div>\n</div>", "solution_html": "<div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px;\">\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"{\\text{NO}} \\bullet {\\text{(g)}} + {{\\text{O}}_{\\text{3}}}{\\text{(g)}} \\to {\\text{N}}{{\\text{O}}_{\\text{2}}} \\bullet {\\text{(g)}} + {{\\text{O}}_{\\text{2}}}{\\text{(g)}}\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n<mrow>\n<mtext>NO</mtext>\n</mrow>\n<mo>∙</mo>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>(g)</mtext>\n</mrow>\n<mo>+</mo>\n<mrow>\n<msub>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>O</mtext>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>3</mtext>\n</mrow>\n</msub>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>(g)</mtext>\n</mrow>\n<mo stretchy=\"false\">→</mo>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>N</mtext>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<msub>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>O</mtext>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>2</mtext>\n</mrow>\n</msub>\n</mrow>\n<mo>∙</mo>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>(g)</mtext>\n</mrow>\n<mo>+</mo>\n<mrow>\n<msub>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>O</mtext>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>2</mtext>\n</mrow>\n</msub>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>(g)</mtext>\n</mrow>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=